data.description: BRAND NEW ROOF!! Discover the perfect blend of comfort and convenience in this charming 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom townhome nestled in the highly sought-after community of Northbrook Village! With its impressive volume ceilings, this residence offers a spacious and welcoming ambiance from the moment you step inside. The heart of the home is a generously sized living room featuring a cozy wood-burning fireplace, making it an ideal place to relax and entertain. Two of the bedrooms are conveniently located on the main level, providing flexibility for various living arrangements. Ascend to the second level to find the luxurious master suite, complete with a private master bath and a roomy walk-in closet, offering you a retreat of your own. Storage is a breeze with a handy closet located underneath the staircas ensuring you have room for all your essentials. Also the attached 2-car garage provides not only secure parking but additional storage solutions. Step outside to the screened-in porch that overlooks the spacious backyard, a serene oasis for outdoor enjoyment and gatherings. With Ormond Beach Middle School just a stone's throw away, this home is perfectly situated for families seeking educational convenience. Don't miss the opportunity to make this delightful townhome your own. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and experience all that Northbrook Village living has to offer. Square footage received from tax rolls. All information deemed accurate but can not be guaranteed. Furniture negotiable!
